abstract static class DatumUtils.Accessor.ByReference<L extends Datum.Layout> extends DatumUtils.Accessor<ByteBuffer,L>
Abstract superclass of accessors for by-reference types.

There are always length-specific accessors for each length through 8, even in 4-byte-datum builds, plus accessors for fixed lengths greater than 8, cstrings, and varlenas.
